Yes 👍 you can professionally combine loading + formatting + validation into one clean function. This is actually common in agent systems when prompt usage is simple.

We will make one function:

get_final_prompt(text)

which will:
	1.	Connect Phoenix
	2.	Load prompt
	3.	Validate template
	4.	Inject text
	5.	Return final prompt

